  2→//!
  3→//! These map the known shape of `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (JSON5) and
  4→//! related files into typed Rust structs. Uses `#[serde(default)]`
  5→//! liberally for forward-compatibility with unknown OpenClaw versions.
